quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"Mong`a hau U ile A bitsa Moshe: “Tsamaea o ee ho batho ba etsang liphoso"
  26,11,“Batho ba Faro. Na ba tla ts’aba Allah?”
  26,12,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ke t`saba hore ba tloha ba mphara ka leshano"
  26,13,"“Sefuba sa ka se tla petatsana. Puo ea ka e se hlake, kahoo nthome le Aarone"
  26,14,"“Ba bile ba na le qoso ea tlolo ea molao khahlano le ‘na, ka hona ke t`saba hore ba se tlohe ba mpolaea.”"
  26,15,"Allah A re: “Leletho, Tsoelang pele, bobeli ba lona ka lits’upiso tsa Rona. Ruri! Re tlabale lona, le hona ho le mamela"
  26,16,"“Joale, tsamaeang ‘moho le ee ho Faro, le re: “Re rometsoe ke ‘Maballi le Mong`a mafats’e ho uena"
  26,17,“Lokolla bana ba Israele ho tsamaea le rona.”
  26,18,"Faro a re: “Na ha re’a u holisa o le ngoana har’a rona? Oa lula lilemo tse ngata le rona bophelong ba hau"
  26,19,"“Eaba o etsa ketso eo u kileng oa e etsa, eo u e tsebang, oa ba e mong oa ba hlokang teboho!”"
  26,20,"Moshe a re: “Ke entse, nakong eo ke neng ke le ka har’a ba khelohileng"
  26,21,"“Ka lebaka la ho le t`saba ka baleha, Empa Mong`a ka U ile a nts’usumetsa ka taelo esita le hona ho nkhetha ke le e mong oa baromuoa ba Hae"
  26,22,"“Joale, sena ke ke tsela eo u mputsang ka eona, u nts’eolla ka hore: ke entse bana ba Israele makhoba.”"
  26,23,"Faro a re: “Joale, ke eng ‘Maballi le Mong`a mafats’e?”"
  26,24,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e le lintho tsohle tse teng lipakeng tsa ona, – haeba u batla ho rua tsebo.”"
  26,25,"Eaba faro o re ho ba neng ba mo pota-potile: “Na le’a utloa?”"
  26,26,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a lona le bo-ntat’a lona ho tloha ts’imolohong.”"
  26,27,"Faro a re: “Ruri! Moromuoa enoa ea romeletsoeng ho lona e feela e le lehlanya!”"
  26,28,"Moshe a re: “Mong`a bochabela le bophirima le tsohle tse lipakeng tsa tsona, ha feela ebale na le kutloisiso.”"
  26,29,"Faro a re: “Ha feela eba u ka ikhethela molimo e mong ntle ho ‘na, Ruri! Ke tla u koala chankaneng.”"
  26,30,"Moshe a re: “Le hoja ke u bonts’a se seng se hlakileng?”"
  26,31,"Faro a re: “Se bonts’e, haeba u e mong oa ba nang le ‘nete!”"
  26,32,"Eaba Moshe o akhela lere la hae fats’e, la fetoha noha"
  26,33,"A pholla lehlakore ka letsoho la hae, eaba le hlaha le le lesoeu ho babohi"